{"tid":373024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嘩𨳒, 我識人聽日可能仲要過澳門做嘢.","createTime":"2017-08-24T17:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T18:03:16.000Z","uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4877546c44d488c406d4d7a453638ec4ba77b447","tid":373024,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"黐孖筋! 佢澳門嗰面嘅同事都話而家澳門好亂, 啲住宅玻璃爛晒, 吹走晒啲人落街. 政府隱瞞死亡人數. 佢話亂到好似世界末日咁. 當地又冇食水, 救援措施又廢. 我就即刻諗到, 萬一之後有啲咩未知嘅連鎖效應發生真係會死人㗎喎. <br />\n<br />\n當事人個上司聽完個澳門同事話當地有幾亂同危險之後, 個上司就話咩出發前買份保險咪得喎...... 而家個當事人仲同個上司傾緊. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜而家嘅保險業先進到可以保埋命㗎嗱? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b6913e91c91f2ffe9ae0711c1850dca711af07","tid":373024,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"有冇當地人講吓而家情況點? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f51068ad4842606d377fd5f25caf229bf90efa3","tid":373024,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdc8783edc13903073a296b5119dd4d15318507","tid":373024,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5952ea0bf1989de4322f1719f8fc9b05f68c1b2","tid":373024,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"群組消息：‼️最新消息：下環街同司打口會劃為疫區，今晚衛生署會派人去曬消毒藥水，街邊既臭味全部是細菌，吸入會引起身體狀況不佳，請老弱婦孺盡量避免入下環街司打口。<br />\n叫朋友不要來"},{"pid":"e5f300a6a86c03b3ed6c0a6fbf73ffa54e23f5a6","tid":373024,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"叫你同事托幾箱維他水過去啦<br />\n上樓大計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f377d024a3f55e286a962734162b9374c50bc6c2","tid":373024,"uid":37125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc